    "causal_summary": "Our cli-* dispatch surface (`cli-devin` for SWE-1.6, `cli-opencode` for DeepSeek-v4-pro / Kimi-k2.6 / Qwen3.6 / GLM-5.1) and `sk-prompt`'s framework selection got measurably better through the 113 arc — RCAF default, medium pre-plan, standard bundle-gate, cross-model validation. But that arc optimized **prompt composition**. We have not yet addressed **runtime patterns** that small models need to produce reliable output: token-aware context budgets, output verification pipelines, per-model profile registries, escalation policies, and structured (non-prose) permission boundaries.",
